				<div class="book-name">The Third Book of Kings </div>
				<div class="act-chapter">
					<div class="prev-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020195305/http://catholicbible.online/knox/OT/3_Kgs/7131">&lt; prev</a></div>|
					<div class="chapter">Chapter 3</div>
					|<div class="next-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020195305/http://catholicbible.online/knox/OT/3_Kgs/7133">next &gt;</a></div>
